data.description: Amazing single story home featuring an open floorplan and plenty of windows bringing in the natural light. Located in the beautiful community of Gladden Farms. This floorplan consists of 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths with 2 of the bedrooms being suites with their own bathrooms in addition to a 3rd bedroom and a full bathroom in the hallway.  The kitchen opens to the great room and dining area with granite countertops, plenty of cabinet space and storage.  Back Patio and yard perfect for those family get togethers with the build in bbq , big patio and mature yard! Come see and make this property your next home! Allow 48 hours for response.
